Erik Dellums https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erik_Dellums 0 Erik Todd Dellums is an American actor, voice actor, and narrator. He played the drug kingpin Luther Mahoney for two seasons on Homicide: Life on the Street and voiced the roles as the radio DJ Three-Dog in the 2008 video game Fallout 3 and the main antagonist, Prince Arcann in Knights of the Fallen Empire, the 2015 expansion to Star Wars: The Old Republic.
